 compact but efficient, with direct access to the garden outside. Clerestory windows ensure consistent, indirect light throughout the day while preserving privacy from the street.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-pass-through-window-080625-742-12.jpg\" alt=\"The kitchen sits at the heart of the southern volume and shares space with the dining area. It is compact but efficient, with direct access to the garden outside via a pass-through window. Clerestory windows ensure consistent, indirect light throughout the day while preserving privacy from the street.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-pass-through-window-080625-742-12.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-pass-through-window-080625-742-12-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-pass-through-window-080625-742-12-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-pass-through-window-080625-742-12-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-pass-through-window-080625-742-12-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-kitchen-pass-through-window-080625-742-13.jpg\" alt=\"The kitchen sits at the heart of the southern volume and shares space with the dining area. It is compact but efficient, with direct access to the garden outside via a pass-through window. Clerestory windows ensure consistent, indirect light throughout the day while preserving privacy from the street.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/upload