w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe family room doubles as a theater with built-in acoustic treatments and a sound system. Other rooms serve dual purposes: the guest room also functions as a workout area, and two craft rooms can be combined via a sliding partition. This flexible approach to program keeps the layout compact but responsive.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-living-room-play-room-080625-743-15.jpg\" alt=\"The family room doubles as a theater with built-in acoustic treatments and a sound system. Other rooms serve dual purposes: the guest room also functions as a workout area, and two craft rooms can be combined via a sliding partition. This flexible approach to program keeps the layout compact but responsive.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-living-room-play-room-080625-743-15.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-living-room-play-room-080625-743-15-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-living-room-play-room-080625-743-15-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-living-room-play-room-080625-743-15-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-living-room-play-room-080625-743-15-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-living-room-play-room-glass-wall-080625-743-16.jpg\" alt=\"The family room doubles as a theater with built-in acoustic treatments and a sound system. Other rooms serve dual purposes: the guest room also functions as a workout area, and two craft rooms can be combined via a sliding partition. This flexible approach to program keeps the layout compact but responsive.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-living-room-play-room-glass-wall-080625-743-16.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-living-room-play-room-glass-wall-080625-743-16-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-living-room-play-room-glass-wall-080625-743-16-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-living-room-play-room-glass-wall-080625-743-16-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-living-room-play-room-glass-wall-080625-743-16-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eExplore the home through the architectural drawings.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1152\" height=\"817\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-house-design-080625-744-17.jpg\" alt=\"Explore this modern home through the architectural drawings.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-house-design-080625-744-17.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-house-design-080625-744-17-940x667.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-house-design-080625-744-17-800x567.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-house-design-080625-744-17-768x545.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1152px) 100vw, 1152px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1772\" height=\"2375\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-house-floor-plans-080625-744-18.jpg\" alt=\"Explore this modern home through the architectural drawings.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-house-floor-plans-080625-744-18.jpg 1772w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-house-floor-plans-080625-744-18-940x1260.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-house-floor-plans-080625-744-18-800x1072.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-house-floor-plans-080625-744-18-768x1029.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-house-floor-plans-080625-744-18-1146x1536.jpg 1146w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-house-floor-plans-080625-744-18-1528x2048.jpg 1528w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1772px) 100vw, 1772px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eBroadview Residence is built for longevity, not show. Every element supports flexible living, natural light, and long-term comfort, proving that thoughtful design can work within real-world limits.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography: \u003ca href=\"https://www.sozinhoimagery.com/\"\u003eSozinho Imagery\u003c/a\u003e | Architecture: KO Architecture| Structural: BTL Engineering | Surveyor: DOWL HKM | Contractor: NRC Homes\u003c/h6\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
